  "instructions": [
    "Heat vegetable oil in a large wok or frying pan over medium heat.",
    "Add minced garlic and grated ginger and cook, stirring constantly, for 30 seconds.",
    "Add sake, soy sauce, sambal oelek, and 2 cups vegetable broth, and cook, stirring constantly, for 30 seconds.",
    "Add rice noodles and cook, stirring constantly, for 2 minutes.",
    "Add Chinese broomcorn, peeled daikon, bean sprouts, scallions, and sesame seeds, and cook, stirring constantly, for 2 minutes.",
    "Add salt and black pepper to taste, and stir-fry for an additional minute.",
    "Transfer noodles to a serving platter and garnish with green onions, sesame seeds, and sesame oil.",
    "Drizzle with rice vinegar and serve with chili flakes, curry powder, and cornstarch mixture on the side.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!",
    "Garnish with lime wedges and serve to your guests.",
    "Make sure to garnish with green onions and sesame seeds for a festive touch."
